{"tid":664933,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"平時泛民做柒事，班自稱毒派的五毛狗就追住黎咬，你班五毛狗柒就以笑遮醜。","createTime":"2018-05-14T13:33:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T10:01:20.000Z","uid":27451,"like":14,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4d3b0117dbb2de17ceb0d4667b606f5529eec628","tid":664933,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T13:33:35.000Z","msg":"除撚左搵五毛關呢d小醜出黎屈毛，週圍結怨摟屌貼大字報洗版，你班柒班以為人多就蝦蝦霸霸，衰撚左重要開貼狂打飛機，你班五毛狗走撚出連登有撚人識你咩，唔撚好講話支持啦。"},{"pid":"141c9b829302fda036bda39a53ee21d516fd47ef","tid":664933,"uid":47359,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T13:36:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛未來撚啊廢扮泛民打手<br />\n實質同其他五毛一唱一和<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/07/122237_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2F122237_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=778b9c09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/07/122311_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2F122311_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=b4780c6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/07/122316_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2F122316_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=418df5ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"7040831e49291498bcf1d139c82c7992f9bfcea7","tid":664933,"uid":27451,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T13:36:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除撚左搵五毛關呢d小醜出黎屈毛，週圍結怨摟屌貼大字報洗版，你班柒人以為人多就蝦蝦霸霸，衰撚左重要開貼狂打飛機，你班五毛狗走撚出連登有撚人識你咩，唔撚好講話支持啦。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"802ec60327b2a82df0451647ad098c5eeefcd2ed","tid":664933,"uid":27451,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20